1.  
    
    <div id="kFootBsktc1832">
    
    <div class="footBskt_itti">
    
    Library
    
    </div>
    
    <div class="footBskt_itco">
    
    <div>
    
    <div class="dk_definitionMeta_def">
    
    A library is a set of tools, or framework, used by an application –
    like OM – to execute specific tasks.
    
    </div>
    
    </div>
    
    </div>
    
    </div>

